column2: Strengths: Strategic thinkers, logical, future-oriented, and independent. Weaknesses: May seem overly critical, emotionally distant, and stubborn.
Strengths: Analytical, abstract thinkers, innovative, and logical. Weaknesses: Can be detached, indecisive, and struggle with practical matters.
Strengths: Confident leaders, decisive, efficient, and strategic. Weaknesses: Can be dominating, insensitive, and overly focused on work.
Strengths: Innovative, curious, great debaters, and problem-solvers. Weaknesses: May be argumentative, easily bored, and non-conformist.
Strengths: Insightful, principled, moral, and empathetic. Weaknesses: Can be overly idealistic, sensitive, and perfectionistic.
Strengths: Idealistic, empathetic, guided by core values, and creative. Weaknesses: Can be impractical, overly emotional, and avoid conflict.
Strengths: Charismatic, inspiring, natural leaders, and community-focused. Weaknesses: Can be overly selfless, manipulative, and struggle with criticism.
Strengths: Enthusiastic, creative, value freedom, and individualistic. Weaknesses: Can be easily distracted, lack focus, and struggle with follow-through.
Strengths: Responsible, methodical, dutiful, and organized. Weaknesses: Can be rigid, inflexible, and struggle with change.
Strengths: Nurturing, dependable, loyal, and detail-oriented. Weaknesses: Can be overly humble, resistant to change, and avoid confrontation.
Strengths: Organized, efficient, value tradition, and strong-willed. Weaknesses: Can be stubborn, insensitive, and overly controlling.
Strengths: Warm, caring, socially harmonious, and supportive. Weaknesses: Can be needy, approval-seeking, and struggle with criticism.
Strengths: Pragmatic, flexible, hands-on, and independent. Weaknesses: Can be aloof, risk-taking, and struggle with planning.
Strengths: Gentle, sensitive, value harmony, and creative. Weaknesses: Can be overly modest, unpredictable, and avoid conflict.
Strengths: Energetic, perceptive, action-oriented, and adventurous. Weaknesses: Can be impulsive, risk-prone, and struggle with long-term planning.
Strengths: Outgoing, spontaneous, live in the moment, and enjoy life. Weaknesses: Can be attention-seeking, easily bored, and avoid responsibilities.
